title: Statistical Genomics in Breast Cancer
description: Integrating GWAS, eQTL, and RNA-seq data to uncover genetic drivers and expression patterns in TNBC subtypes.

title: Recipe and Rating: Analysis of Calories
description: Analyzed 83,782 recipes to study the relationship between calorie counts, ingredients, and user ratings on food.com.

title: RStudio Server Setup on HPC
description: Configured a containerized RStudio Server on Scripps Research HPC cluster using Singularity for large-scale data analysis.

title: PIPseq Analysis of Neural Subtypes
description: Developed scRNA-seq pipelines with Seurat and Slingshot to characterize OPC and MOL subpopulations and pseudotime trajectories.

title: Hippocampal Sequential Events Modeling
description: Analyzed hippocampal ensemble activity using standardized firing patterns to decode sequential nonspatial event representations.

title: Diffusion Pseudotime Analysis of OPCs
description: Applied diffusion maps and rank-based pseudotime extraction to trace the lineage progression of naive OPCs.
